      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;audio-player-wrapper&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;audio-caption&#34;&gt;You can listen to my thoughts!&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;custom-audio-player&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;audio preload=&#34;metadata&#34; class=&#34;audio-element&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;source src=&#34;https://www.abdisalam.blog/audio/desire-evil.m4a&#34; type=&#34;audio/mp4&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;source src=&#34;https://www.abdisalam.blog/audio/desire-evil.m4a&#34; type=&#34;audio/mpeg&#34;&gt;&#xA;            Your browser does not support the audio element.&#xA;        &lt;/audio&gt;&#xA;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;progress-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;progress-bar&#34;&gt;&#xA;                &lt;div class=&#34;progress-fill&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;        &lt;button class=&#34;play-pause-btn&#34; aria-label=&#34;Play&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;play-icon&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34;&gt;&#xA;                &lt;path d=&#34;M8 5v14l11-7z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; /&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;pause-icon&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; style=&#34;display: none;&#34;&gt;&#xA;                &lt;path d=&#34;M6 19h4V5H6v14zm8-14v14h4V5h-4z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; /&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;time-display current-time&#34;&gt;0:00&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;time-display duration&#34;&gt;--:--&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: center; font-style: italic; margin: 30px 0;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#34;The chains of habit are too weak to be felt until they are too strong to be broken.&#34;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;— Samuel Johnson&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Recently, I have been thinking if my desires-good or bad-control me? Desire. It really is one of the greatest walls standing between a man and his own peace. Not all desires are evil, but the moment they become the master, the soul begins to rot. I have come to see more recently, there is something deceptive about it, the way it starts as a whisper(gentle), almost harmless. A itching for ease, for pleasure, for something just out of reach. It does not force itself upon you; it only asks. Wouldn&amp;rsquo;t it be easier? Wouldn&amp;rsquo;t it be nice? What harm is there in just this once? Or What if I just&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
